He did, eventually. For various reasons ... I think this was my mother's fault, she didn't allow the divorce to proceed, and, of course, divorce was very difficult to come by until the sixties.
 And he finally divorced and remarried, although he'd been with Maisie for quite some years before that. I think it was 1961.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 And he didn't have other children himself?
