 for the first couple, two or three years of my life. I was born in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Middlesbrough{\*\xmlclose}, living with my parents for about a year and a half. I was then taken by my mother to join my grandmother in 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Middlesbrough{\*\xmlclose} for another two years or so. And then, at the age of four, we all moved down \_ my mother, grandmother and myself \_ moved down to Pimlico in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname City}}London
{\*\xmlclose}, because {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}London{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} was the only place 
