{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceName}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceName}}Belsize{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceType}}Park{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, to an attic flat, in 
