No, no, you're not at all. I think it's fascinating. But what I was wondering was, I thought you said you were in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Lancaster{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} in 1939.
