\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Peter:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 Yes, not {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname City}}Lancaster{\*\xmlclose}, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}
Blackpool{\*\xmlclose}. My mother was singing on the pier at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Blackpool{\*\xmlclose}
, for three months. Had a wonderful ... I used to have wonderful summers, as a child, because my mother was in concert parties, one year after another, right through the thirties \_ Worthing, Hastings, Llandudno, Blackpool ...
