nerations really. Yes, there may have been rare exceptions. But, by and large, my mother ... [was] very capable of higher education, but never achieved it, and, therefore, didn't really ... you know, but she looked at it from a distance, but she wasn't re
ally a pushing influence.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11733749 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
