icer training course because life as a ... as a private soldier, at Blandford, was a bit, in some respects, quite grim. Perhaps I ought to embellish this by giving you one illustration. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11733749 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 Not at Bland
