a
d frozen solid, and with the gales sweeping in the windows, far below freezing, we had to climb into bed in those circumstances, and I used to go to bed fully clothed, with just my boots off, and we just spread layers and layers of newspaper, to try and g
et warm. And that was it. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11733749 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
