So that sort of experience as a private soldier made me feel that, well, even if ... for a few months, it was better to seek an alternative. So I became, I went in for and succeeded in getting, because of my school education, bec
ame a Royal Army Education Corps sergeant, at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceName}}Buchanan{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceType}}Castle{\*\xmlclose}, near {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place
}}Glasgow{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. And then went in for, because it was expected of all us, went in for this officer training arrangement, which, as I say, I succeeded, but happily turned down, because I knew I was going to Cambridge.
