\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Peter:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 No, no, I haven't changed! No, no. But I think I appreciate more the professional skills of Army d
iscipline, let's say. Let's put it that way. I think it can be done in a, in a shrewd and informed way, more than we used to. We used to think it was just ... you just had to instil obedience, was the idea, I think, in those days. Instilling obedience, wa
s a kind of colonial ...
