\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 Perhaps we should move on now to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}
