urrounding streets. They were usually surrounding streets, and weren't far away. They weren't in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}East Cambridge{\*\xmlclose}
 much. There were the occasional exceptions, where people learned from their lodgings, that's true. 
