nd to Parliament, as well as to all those disability organisations which wanted representation. He was a close friend. He was President of the Students' Union at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Cambridge
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, and when I got to enjoy politics, but I regarded myself as a reporter of politics, at that stage, and still am, I suppose, than a participant. But he was a very, he was a close friend. There were others. 
