a
rned that they were eager, at the new Free University of Berlin, which was set up on the basis of a kind of alternative to the Humboldt, which was in East Berlin - because the Humboldt was there, they decided that a university was needed in West Berlin, a
nd the Free University had just been launched. And they wanted to attract a few people from overseas, and so we had a small group of students from the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname country-region}}United States{\*\xmlclose}
