The third thing I'd like to just mention briefly, is his contribution to our understanding of legal services. He, with a colleague [Robert Stevens], produced two books \_ }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
Lawyers and the Courts}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 , and one on social justice \_ which reviewed the whole development of English law, the whole history and development of English law. And not merely that, provided the 
