\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Peter:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 Not very, is the truth. He had a long\_lasting rela
tionship which his close friends knew about, but were not particularly involved in. I think he was always ... he was still mindful of the possibilities of publicity. He was also mindful of the fact that the prejudices were so deep, this wasn't just a publ
i
c matter, it even affected, let's say, the families of friends. And for a long time, he tried to ... he didn't make the pretence, but he allowed the pretence to be perpetrated that there were some daughters of a famous biscuit family [the Westons] who wer
e interested in him, and, you know, as you go into your twenties and then into your thirties, you can maintain for a long time the idea that, you know, you are heterosexual, when it isn't particularly true.
