\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Peter:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 Oh yes, I was, 
from the beginning. Oh yes. And it was ... I had very friendly relationships with his partner. Although, as I'm trying to say, it wasn't of a kind where I would be involved in holiday jaunts, for example, with he and his partner. They led their life, soci
ally speaking, and we had our very close, very close friendship, separately, on the whole, though, of course, there were occasions when we, you know, saw each other, had a meal together, even. But they were relatively rare. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid15942912 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 And to wind up the relationship
