network. Others, like Julian le Grand, have told stories about him flying across from America and then with only an hour's pause, cooking lunch for six, or cooking dinner for six, and that kind of thing. And there was one great feature of him, which is wo
rth mentioning in an account of somebody's biography, and that was his disarming modesty and quickness. 
