This is again, a social responsibility: to find who are the people who are patients in such places. Are 
they in genuine need of being in such institutions? Are they in the best places? Are they getting the right kind of care? But also, are they happy there? Are they in a situation where they can receive visits if they still have friends or relatives availab
le to come to see them? And obviously that is a task which can't only be left to those who are running this particular nursing Home, but has to be done independently. 
