eport for 1997, which is largely devoted to the subject of poverty. I find myself being very critical of their unwillingness to try to bang heads together and achieve, let's say, a consensus, either scientifically or politically, in defence of this Copenh
agen Agreement to the dual standard of poverty, or International Poverty Line. But at the same time, I'm very pleased ...
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11733749 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
