ctures which would tend to have the influence of pressing everything back into a traditional or well-established mould, rather than breaking free from that mould. And I think we all got very excited by that.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid13858014 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
