{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceName}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Cambridge{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceType}}University{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} which I\rquote d attended in the early fifties.
