 that they could easily block the spine road under the University from delivery of important chemical products and machinery, and a relatively small number could do that, and the police were eventually called in to remove them, and although there were onl
y a dozen students blocking the road on the first occasion, and they were easily removed by the police, as soon as they were removed, the word got round, and because the towers were so handy, and that\rquote 
