\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid3890122 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
So I think that political work I take very seriously, even today. There\rquote s lots of fun in doing it. There is still a sense in which planning, as illustrated by the Labour Party in the 1960s, hasn\rquote 
