{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceType}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}University{\*\xmlclose} of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname PlaceName}}Warwick{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
. He may have recently retired. But he, again, I had enormous respect for him, because he held down a very demanding full-time job, but was also extraordinarily witty and conversational and active in getting around the country, and 
not only following with real skill and perception, causes to do with sight and blindness, but he was a good historian. I\rquote ve no doubt there are others that occur to both of us. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid3890122 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
