m just one of those very lucky people who found somebody relatively late in life, who met every kind of need that one has for male/female relationships. I mean, I feel very lucky. We\rquote ve been together now 18 years, and I hope it goes on some time y
et. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11733749 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 But politically?
