What I think is urgent is that they are too much concerned with what impinges on their consciousness from day to day, rather than from strategic objectives, concerns. And that\rquote s, I think, what the academic has to convey. But in some ways, they
\rquote ve got to meet half way. You\rquote ve got to persuade each of them that the other part of their game plan deserves more attention than it\rquote s been given by them hitherto. So I\rquote 
m saying something very general about my political awareness of this. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11733749 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid3890122 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 It\rquote 
