[politics], although, of course, there are all the light-hearted superficial things that one gains about it. You find that a lot of politicians are human beings, and that some of them can be as lazy as some academics, and some of them can drink as much as
 some academics, and some of them can be as tempted by the other sex as some academics! (LAUGHS) 
