shment, and restoring stained glass windows, so his business has been one which is a mixture of craft as well as collection and sales. Adam has become an acupuncturist. He\rquote s had two important stays in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname country-region}
}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}China{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} to that purpose, but is still at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname Street}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname address}}Mansfield Place{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
