s Organiser in the South-West, and later, she came to be appointed one of the three or four top people in the Labour Party at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname Street}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname address}}Walworth Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, and ran two conferences in the mid-1980s, and the first Conference at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Bournemouth{\*\xmlclose}. So that was a frenetic responsibility, in a sense, which I learned about subsequently. 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid11733749 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 
