\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10294858\charrsid10294858 Peter:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 Yes. I do nearly all the shopping for the household. And that\rquote 
