m very lucky, because I can fit in with this, I can often drive up with Jean at Monday lunch time, or just after, to Parliament, and we\rquote ll share the driving, but I\rquote 
m pleased to do that, partly because I can drive her around in London when we go back to our London home, because we have to have one, which happens to be in Peckham, a tiny little terraced house, really only big enough for two people. And I d
o the shopping there, and I do it each morning, I get the milk and the paper and so on. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s22\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid5648674 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11733749\charrsid10294858 And that\rquote 
