 I fit in with that as a sort of slightly less efficient do-it-yourself merchant. And, for instance, in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns3{\factoidname place}}Ireland{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, I\rquote 
